<L>__{interior burton's house kitchen morning}
<A>__{burton, hung over, staggering into the kitchen of his home, stopping dead. a newspaper is set beside his coffee pot. a front page of the washington post. years back. the lead article reports that a siege has been successfully broken burton, bloody and wounded, is being carried to an ambulance. a hero. across the top these words have been written: how did this happen, you gutless fuck? burton stares. steaming.}
